| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3995 — Recovery Inhibition (kraken)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 16a0ea9a-b00b-52e0-be75-522de59c12ad"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
